		<title>Creating a Killer Task Management Workflow</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/KylesRandom/~3/s-QzrSFP5fE/</link>
		<comments>http://kylesrandom.com/2011/07/killer-workflow/#comments</comments>
